Name: Billy
About the game: Billy is a fun puzzle game in which you control two characters that help each other by mastering a switching mechanic that helps you reach new places. Ultra fast respawns keep the pace up as you make your way through a colorful world full of challenging platforming! Can you make it to the end? Contains an autosave feature Original music by M. Lee White
